			TODO for ELusive CSS Parser

General:
--------

* Check up on CSS discussions from links-discuss mailing list. They contain
  info about how to convert different units. This is renderer stuff however.

* In the interface function parse() the loop 'while (*len)' will not make it
  possible to have a last token correctly used since it will stop there not
  calling the lower parser even though it might not need more input.

* Make mediatype bitmap entries public and util functions mediatype for
  converting/adding them to the stylesheet.

	css_add_mediatype(stylesheet_node, "tty");
  or
	css_add_mediatype(stylesheet_node, str2mediatype("tty"));

* The interface function done() should set len pointer to -1 and have the
  state parsers clean up after themselves.

